on Playbook]]'' (2017\u201318).<ref>{{Cite web|first=Na-kyung|last=Kim|url=https://www.hankyung.com/entertainment/article/201912038551I|title='\uc2ac\uae30\ub85c\uc6b4 \uc758\uc0ac\uc0dd\ud65c', \uc774\ubc88\uc5d4 \ubcd1\uc6d0\uc774\ub2e4\u2026\ub300\ubcf8\ub9ac\ub529 \ud604\uc7a5 \uacf5\uac1c|date=December 3, 2019|website=Hankyung|lang=ko|accessdate=January 25, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Original soundtrack==\n{{Infobox album\n| name         = Hospital Playlist OST\n| type         = [[soundtrack]]\n| artist       = Various Artists\n| cover        = \n| alt          = \n| released     = 2020\n| studio       = \n| genre        = [[Soundtrack]]\n| language     = {{hlist|[[Korean language|Korean]]|[[English language|English]]}}\n| label        = {{hlist|Studio Maeum C|Egg is Coming|[[Genie Music|Genie]]|[[Stone Music Entertainment|Stone]]}}\n| producer     = \n}}\n\n===Part 1===\n{{tracklist\n| headline = Released on {{start date|2020|3|13}}\n| extra_column = Artist\n| title1 = Lonely Night\n| note1 = \n| lyrics1 = [[Kim Tae-won]]\n| music1 = Kim Tae-won\n| extra1 = [[Kwon Jin-ah]]{{efn|Original song by [[Boohwal]], released in 1997.}}\n| length1 = 4:04\n| title2 = Lonely Night\n| note2 = Inst.\n| music2 = Kim Tae-won\n| length2 = 4:04\n| total_length = 8:08\n}}\n\n===Part 2===\n{{tracklist\n| headline = Released on {{start date|2020|3|20}}\n| extra_column = Artist\n| title1 = Introduce Me a Good Person\n| note1 = \uc88b\uc740 \uc0ac\ub78c \uc788\uc73c\uba74 \uc18c\uac1c\uc2dc\ucf1c\uc918 \n| lyrics1 = Kim Hee-tam\n| music1 = [[Jung Jae-hyung]]\n| extra1 = [[Joy (singer)|Joy]] ([[Red Velvet (band)|Red Velvet]]){{efn|Original song by Basis, released in 1996.}}\n| length1 = 3:08\n| title2 = Introduce Me a Good Person\n| note2 = Inst.\n| music2 = Jung Jae-hyung\n| length2 = 3:08\n| total_length = 6:16\n}}\n\n===Part 3===\n{{tracklist\n| headline = Released on {{start date|2020|3|27}}\n| extra_column = Artist\n| title1 = Aloha\n| note1 = \uc544\ub85c\ud558\n| lyrics1 = Kim Tae-hoon