, released in 1993.}}\n| length1 = 4:05\n| title2 = You Always\n| note2 = Inst.\n| music2 = Park Jung-won\n| length2 = 4:05 \n| total_length = 8:10\n}}\n\n===Chart performance===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:26em;\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:2em;\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Peak<br />positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:5em;\" | Remarks\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Ref.\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Gaon Digital Chart|KOR]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Lonely Night\" <small>([[Kwon Jin-ah]])</small>\n| rowspan=6| 2020\n| 70\n| Part 1\n| rowspan=6| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=16&hitYear=2020&termGbn=week|title=2020 Week 16 Digital Chart|accessdate=April 23, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Introduce Me a Good Person\" <small>([[Joy (singer)|Joy]])</small>\n| 12\n| Part 2\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Aloha\" <small>([[Jo Jung-suk]])</small>\n| 1\n| Part 3\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Confession Is Not Flashy\" <small>([[Cho Kyu-hyun|Kyuhyun]])</small>\n| 65\n| Part 4\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Beautiful My Love\" <small>([[Urban Zakapa]])</small>\n| 45\n| Part 5\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"In Front of City Hall at the Subway Station\" <small>([[Kwak Jin-eon]])</small>\n| 141\n| Part 6\n|-\n|}\n\n==Ratings==\nIn this table, {{color|blue|'''the blue numbers'''}} represent the lowest ratings and {{color|red|'''the red numbers'''}} represent the highest ratings.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n! rowspan=\"3\" | {{abbr|Ep.|Episode}}\n! rowspan=\"3\" | Original broadcast date\n! colspan=\"3\" | Average audience share\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" | AGB Nielsen<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nielsenkorea.co.kr/tv_terrestrial_day.asp?menu=Tit_1&sub_menu=3_1&area=00&begin_date=20200312|title=Nielsen Korea|work=AGB Nielsen Media Research|langua